    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited as a project car or for parts. It currently has major mechanical issues, including a severe engine knock and a transmission that requires a full rebuild. The exterior shows significant rust on the rocker panels and several large dents, while the interior has heavy wear and some non-functional electronics. It will likely need to be towed from its current location, but it could be a valuable resource for someone with the right tools and time.",
