    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows its age in several areas. The engine and transmission are functional, but you may notice some minor fluid seepage and a slight hesitation during cold starts. The exterior has a few noticeable scratches and minor dings, while the interior shows typical wear on the upholstery and some fading on the dashboard plastics. Most electronic features work, though the rear power windows are slow to operate. It is a solid choice for someone needing dependable transportation who doesn't mind a bit of character and cosmetic imperfections.",
      "price": 19500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
